<h2 id="2first-of-type">2、:first-of-type</h2>

<p>:first-of-type 表示一组兄弟元素中指定类型的第一个元素</p>

<div class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>/* :first-of-type 选择在父元素中第一个出现的 .square
而不管其在兄弟内的位置如何，第一个正方形有背景色 */
<span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"list"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;</span>.square 这是一个p标签<span class="nt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/div&gt;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-css highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nc">.square</span><span class="nd">:first-of-type</span><span class="p">{</span>
     <span class="nl">background</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="no">orangered</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>效果如下：</p>

