<h2 id="3last-child">3、:last-child</h2>

<p>:last-child 表示在一组兄弟元素中的最后一个元素（类似 :first-child）</p>

<div class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>/* :last-child 此时选中的是最后一个 .square
最后一个正方形有背景色 */
<span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"list"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/div&gt;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-css highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nc">.square</span><span class="nd">:last-child</span><span class="p">{</span>
     <span class="nl">background</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="no">orangered</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

