<h2 id="5not">5、:not</h2>

<p>:not 一个否定伪类，用于匹配不符合参数选择器的元素</p>

<div class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>/* 不含有 .not 的正方形有背景色*/
<span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"list"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square not"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square not"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/div&gt;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-css highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nc">.square</span><span class="nd">:not</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="nc">.not</span><span class="o">)</span><span class="p">{</span>
     <span class="nl">background</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="no">orangered</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>效果如下：</p>

