<h2 id="6nth-childanb">6、:nth-child(an+b)</h2>

<p>:nth-child 这个 CSS 伪类首先会找到当前元素的兄弟元素，然后按照位置的先后顺序从1开始排序，选择的结果为第（an+b）个元素的集合（n=0，1，2，3…）。如果 an+b 为 0，无法选中任何元素</p>

<h3 id="6-1nth-child4-匹配位置为-4-的元素">6-1、:nth-child(4) 匹配位置为 4 的元素</h3>

<div class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>/*第 3 个正方形有背景色 因为第 3 个正方形在所有兄弟元素中排第 4 */
<span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"list"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;</span>.square 这是一个p标签<span class="nt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/div&gt;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-css highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nc">.square</span><span class="nd">:nth-child</span><span class="o">(</span><span class="nt">4</span><span class="o">)</span> <span class="p">{</span>
     <span class="nl">background</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="no">orangered</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>效果如下：</p>

<p><img src="https://lien-1258580758.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/blog-img/11_css-selectors/8.png" alt="img" /></p>

<div class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code> /*此时第 4 个正方形有背景色 */
<span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"list"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
