<h2 id="5selection">5、::selection</h2>

<p>::selection 用于文档中被用户高亮的部分（比如使用鼠标或其他选择设备选中的部分）</p>

<div class="language-html highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"list"</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;div</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">"square"</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</span>
     <span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;</span>.square 这是一个p标签<span class="nt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>
<span class="nt">&lt;/div&gt;</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-css highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="nt">p</span><span class="nd">::selection</span><span class="p">{</span>
     <span class="nl">background-color</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="m">#ffeb3b</span><span class="p">;</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

