<h1 id="兼容性">兼容性</h1>

<h2 id="伪类的兼容性">伪类的兼容性：</h2>

<p><img src="https://lien-1258580758.cos.ap-shanghai.myqcloud.com/blog-img/11_css-selectors/21.png" alt="img" /></p>

